narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this class to non-science people because it is very interesting based on the topics covered but I don't feel like enough of the science was discussed.
It's a super easy class with some really interesting stuff. But it does conflict with many things, being a large chunk of time on Friday afternoon.Especially enjoyed Baltay's module on astronomy.
Yes if want wide overview of variety of topics in science
